# Business Rules Kritis — Musik KITA

## Pendaftaran & Trial

- Trial gratis 1 sesi, durasi **30 menit semua tipe paket**
- Trial HADIR → honor penuh | NO-SHOW → honor **Rp 0** (TRIAL_NS)
- Registrasi Rp 250.000 wajib saat aktif | Murid aktif = registrasi + SPP bulan 1 lunas
- Kids Class min 3 anak; kuota <3 → status menunggu, tidak kena SPP
- Skip trial → langsung Aktif, **wajib reason** (walk_in|migrasi|reaktivasi|lulus_kids)

## Penjadwalan

- Generate sesi otomatis dari jadwal mingguan | Min 3, max 4 sesi/murid/bulan
- Libur tanpa replacement_date → sesi LIBUR saja | Dengan replacement_date → LIBUR + pengganti
- Minggu ke-5 tidak reguler (max 4 counter) kecuali replacement session
- Murid bayar penuh meski hanya 3 sesi
- Pindah jadwal mingguan tetap **boleh dalam bulan yang sama**
- RescheduleService: cek konflik guru + ruang | Admin input via mini-modal absensi
- Holiday Internal → honor Rp 0, replacement_date NULL

## Absensi

- Reschedule izin: info ≥5 jam + izin **pertama** bulan ini
- Izin ke-2+ → video pengganti | Info <5 jam/tanpa info → HANGUS
- Guru pengganti → honor ke substitute_teacher_id
- Libur nasional → honor guru dibayar penuh (kecuali Internal is_honor_paid=false)

## Tagihan & Denda

- SPP auto-generate tgl 1 | Tempo 1-10 | Denda Rp 5.000/hari mulai tgl 11
- Lunas = SPP + seluruh denda | Tunggakan >1 bulan → auto-mundur
- INV/YYYY/MM/NNNN, KW/YYYY/MM/NNNN (reset per bulan)
- Void payment → **Owner only** | Metode: CASH, TRANSFER, QRIS, DEBIT

## Honor Guru

Formula dasar: `harga_paket × 50% / 4`

| Kode | Skenario | Honor |
|------|----------|-------|
| H_REG | Hadir/telat | formula dasar |
| H_TRIAL | Trial hadir | sama H_REG |
| TRIAL_NS | Trial no-show | Rp 0 |
| H_VIDEO | Izin video | sama H_REG |
| H_LIBUR | Libur nasional tanpa replacement | full pay |
| H_HANGUS | No-show/hangus | full pay |
| H_PENG | Guru pengganti | ke pengganti |
| H_KIDS | Kids Class | murid × Rp 42.500 |
| H_UJIAN | Pengawas ujian | Rp 250.000 flat |
| H_IZIN | IZIN_RESCHEDULE original | Rp 0 (honor via sesi pengganti) |
| H_SPLIT | Split reschedule | formula / 2 |

Cut-off honor: **H-2 sebelum akhir bulan**. Slip event: honor event + transport (manual) + lain-lain (manual + keterangan).

## Multi-Kelas

- Murid boleh banyak enrollment ACTIVE bersamaan (contoh: Piano + Gitar)
- `is_primary` = kelas utama (UI/display) — **bukan** filter SPP
- SPP auto-generate tgl 1 untuk **setiap enrollment ACTIVE** (1 kelas = 1 invoice/bulan)
- Multi-kelas: 2 enrollment ACTIVE → 2 invoice SPP terpisah; denda per invoice independen
- Skip SPP: TRIAL, ON_LEAVE/INACTIVE/COMPLETED, paket KIDS_CLASS_BUNDLE (cicilan 3 termin)
- Semua enrollment COMPLETED/INACTIVE → murid auto mundur

## Cuti

- cuti_from/until diisi | Enrollment → ON_LEAVE | Sesi tidak di-generate
- Biaya Rp 100.000/pengajuan | Perpanjang max 1x (total 2 bulan)

## Diskon Invoice

- DISKON ke invoice UNPAID/PARTIAL | Wajib parent_item_id + discount_reason
- NOMINAL atau PERCENT | Hapus diskon → Owner only

## Status Murid (State Machine)

`Calon → Trial → Aktif → Cuti/Selesai/Mengundurkan Diri`

Transisi valid: Calon→Trial/Aktif(skip), Trial→Aktif/Mundur, Aktif→Cuti/Mundur/Selesai, Cuti→Aktif/perpanjang/Mundur, Selesai→Aktif(re-enroll), Mundur→Aktif(bayar registrasi).

